Start the program
Declare i, j and rows
Input value for rows
Output “*” & start a new line
For integer i from 1 to rows:
  For integer j from 1 to i:
      If j is equal to 1:
         Output “*”
      Else : 
         Output j
  For integer j from i-1 to 1:
     Output j
  Output “*” & start a new line
For integer i from rows-1 to 1:
     For integer j from 1 to i:
      If j is equal to 1:
         Output “*”
      Else : 
         Output j
  For integer j from i-1 to 1:
     Output j
  Output “*” & start a new line
End of program
